@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Choice1

state Choice1 <<choice>>
state Choice2 <<choice>>
state Choice3 <<choice>>
state Merge1 <<choice>>

state "Account Creation" as AccountCreation
AccountCreation : entry / 1 month of usage
AccountCreation : do / Creates Account
AccountCreation : exit / Watch videos

state "Discussion State" as DiscussionState
DiscussionState : entry / Premium Account
DiscussionState : do / Discussion between Admin and User
DiscussionState : exit / End of Discussion

state "Updation" as Updation
Updation : entry / Prepare Timeline/view LIKES
Updation : do / Upload Videos
Updation : exit / View Videos

state "View" as View
View : entry / Previously Updated Videos
View : do / View Videos
View : exit / Save Videos in LIKES

state "Show LIKES" as ShowLikes
ShowLikes : entry / Watch Videos and Save in LIKES
ShowLikes : do / Show the list of LIKES
ShowLikes : exit / Upload Videos based on list

Choice1 --> AccountCreation : [Create Account based on Date of Usage]
Choice1 --> Choice2 : [Upload videos based on LIKES]

Choice2 --> ShowLikes
Choice2 --> Updation

AccountCreation --> Choice3 : [Possibilities]

Choice3 --> DiscussionState
Choice3 --> Merge1

ShowLikes --> Merge1 : [Save Videos in LIKES]
Updation --> Merge1

Merge1 --> View
View --> [*] : [Possibilities]
DiscussionState --> [*]

@enduml